{"tid":1547130,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"惠譽下調香港信貸評級　指自治受侵蝕社會事件致長期損害","createTime":"2019-09-06T14:38:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T23:06:55.000Z","uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"96d3c1fae673f8a8a9da797d63613fd10d4bb827","tid":1547130,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T14:38:17.000Z","msg":"惠譽下調香港信貸評級　指自治受侵蝕社會事件致長期損害<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=361832\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D361832&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2nlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=7d8fb57a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D361832&h=63123e80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=361832</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】評級機構惠譽下調香港主權評級。<br />\n<br />\n惠譽調低香港信貸評級由「AA+」降至「AA」，評級展望「負面」，反映評級有機會再被下調。<br />\n<br />\n惠譽指出，香港自治受侵蝕，社會事件造成長期損害，預期下半年經濟收縮，全年零增長，又估計本年度的財政盈餘接近零水平。"},{"pid":"5082d54ec4a072453d22e830a79fa2716cdaf2f8","tid":1547130,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T14:38:26.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c06306f73e0e32d33552a0e2b48a6e1edd65fdec","tid":1547130,"uid":290761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T14:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A8vAmVU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.